all the very boys and girls will cry out that you are a madman.
When you despatch your wife with a rope, and your mother with poison, are you right in your head ?
Why not ?
You nei­ ther did this at Argos, nor slew your mother with the sword as the mad Orestes did.
What, do you imagine that he ran mad after he had murdered his parent;
